  m_text: "\n\n\n\nThis place is... not what I expected.\LIt's too quiet. Even for
    Antarctica.\LI thought I'd hear wind all the time. But sometimes it's just...
    nothing.\nI hear strange noises from the lab at times, i wonder what the scientists
    are doing in there."
